n?lang=rus\"><small>РСП</small> Искупать, искупление</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"6\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"а\" id=\"note6a\" data-full-marker=\"6а\">\n<p data-aid=\"123552451\" id=\"note6a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/3.13?lang=rus#p13\">Мосия 3:13</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"7\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"а\" id=\"note7a\" data-full-marker=\"7а\">\n<p data-aid=\"123552453\" id=\"note7a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/hosea/13.14?lang=rus#p14\">Ос. 13:14</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/15.8,20?lang=rus#p8\">Мосия 15:8, 20</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"8\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"а\" id=\"note8a\" data-full-marker=\"8а\">\n<p data-aid=\"123552455\" id=\"note8a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/42.15?lang=rus#p15\">Алма 42:15</a>. <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/resurrection?lang=rus\"><small>РСП</small> Воскресение</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"б\" id=\"note8b\" data-full-marker=\"8б\">\n<p data-aid=\"123552457\" id=\"note8b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/25.8?lang=rus#p8\">Ис. 25:8</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/nt/1-cor/15.54-55?lang=rus#p54\">1 Кор. 15:54–55</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/morm/7.5?lang=rus#p5\">Морм. 7:5</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"9\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"а\" id=\"note9a\" data-full-marker=\"9а\">\n<p data-aid=\"123552459\" id=\"note9a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.5-13?lang=rus#p5\">У. и З. 88:5–13</a>. <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/light-light-of-christ?lang=rus\"><small>РСП</small> С